Woke up around 11:30 after being sleep disturbed many of times by dreams which were really really compli-me-cated. Than I ate corn pops. =D And later on for lunch around 1-2ish I had nachos/cheese/beef with mom and we chilled and watched Mew Mew Power. xD It's a huge copy off of Sailor Moon. So I go on Msn and who do I see other than David asking me to go with him and Alex to the mall.<333 So I join them. I get there at 2:57pm 3 minutes before we were supossed to meet and they weren't there so I went and walked around than went back and they were there. About 3:30 David and I went to the Bay while Alex got his hair cut. Ooops.. before that we went to Starbucks and David tried to buy me something but I won!<3 hah. But yeah we walked around and chatted. We tried out the beds haha. Than we went and saw Alex who bought a pair of jeans from the Gap and it took like 10 minutes to pay because he had all these cards and stuff lol. After that we went to HMV and David bought the new HIM cd surprised I didn't listen to HIM. lol. After that, we went into Spencers and looked at stuff. David kept trying to buy me something lol it was funny. My pants got caught on a chair and the thing that takes it head of started moving and I was scared. >.< Than I got picked up, said good bye and now I'm here. The blade is off the lawn mower and my dad said I could drive it around but I'm scared of backing it out of the garage and ending up on the road. Haha knowing me that would happen lol. And the belt is broken so I can't cut the grass until tomorrow night. I guess there's lights on the front too. I don't know who's crazy enough to cut the lawn at night though. jeez.
my words could never have felt so imperfect.

Your lip print left on my neck, your footprint on my rug. Let's not leave here tonight, without, memories of the past.

On my way to the mall tonight my stomach dropped, no particular reason and nothing bad has happend yet, just all week I've felt something bad is about to, and I don't like it. Well I got there and I was like a drifter tonight. I went from one group to another basically the whole night. First with Nicole & Lynne & company. Than with Nick, Cj for a bit. I got a pick-up hug from Walter. It was nice. And later on in the night one from Shane before leaving. I spent a lot of the night wandering around by myself. It was nice, but I felt upset and people kept asking me if I was upset. I went and watched the band at Chapters play for a bit. Somehow my feet kept taking me back there. I talked to Dave Sadi and Brian jagjklsdag for a bit. I've decided to just give her $15 for her b-day so she can buy herself something nice. ^.^ On one of my many trips to Chapters while looking around I saw Alex and David heading in. =D I chilled with them for about an hour and a half which was pretty awesome. I ended up buying David his Starbucks. Alex was too full for Taco bell but he got his hair gel. haha. David bought a kickass leather black studded belt. And than they left and I gave them both hugs. Of course lol. I got a lot of hugs tonight. It picked me up. I saw Brynn too. That like, made my night oober special. We have come to the conclusion we are just too awesome to handle. haha. So I didn't get picked up until 10 because my dad forgot about me. Yup haha. And I'm going to take guitar lessons now and Corey bought me 40$ strap. ^_^ We drove Sean home and him and Mark might be stopping by tomorrow. Anyone want to hang out before 6? I'm done. love you<3 You say it's obvious, I say I hope so.
An amazing ending to the night.<3

This world has a cruel and unusual punishment.
I find it hard to believe that,
after so long
of wanting to tell him how I feel,
my feelings are no longer as strong.
Now all I feel for you,
is friendship.
Which I want to be more,
because I know somewhere inside,
it's there.
Hiding, hoping I forget,
I ever liked you at all.
Can't you see?
I'm scared of you and me.
I don't know what's better or worse.
Knowing how I feel,
or not understanding,
these mixed emotions.
Maybe I'm better off alone than with someone,
I will only end up confusing.

Building up a wall.. just to have it thrown down on top of it's creater.
Not knowing what hit them.
All of a sudden.
Every little truth has now turned into a lie.
Every promise is forgotten and mixed into unspoken words.
Every tear shed because you were betrayed falls and stains a cheek for a split second, before it is wiped away, and before anyone can see, that a smile is nothing but fake.. and it hides the truth behind your eyes.
Perfecting it has become a dayly ritual.
Leaving everything behind, and bottling in your problems, has stuck inside for years before and years to come. Slowly but surely the wall crumbles down.. and everything that was worked so hard on, to keep inside, slowly leaked away, and the lies that were told to become the unknown truth and everyone around suddenly realizing they were betrayed, leave the wall to bury it's creater and all it's lies and broken promises. And for every one, another brick fell, until some sense was finally knocked into them.
By then, they were dead, and no apology from them could bring him back from the dead life that was created.

Kicking every dog && cat you saw, causing them to run away and cower. Only making you feel lonelier. Causing every kick, to hurt a little more. Eventually leaving marks. You were watching the kids at the playground, loathing.. or was it envying, their constant bullying.
